    <Description Value="Lazarus AI Suite: Native components for OpenAI ChatGPT integration, local weighted token graph classifiers for explainable NLP, neural networks, industrial Modbus/Siemens PLC gateways, voice synthesizers, and automated PDF/Word document generators."/>
